{"article_id":"PYZHkWQ6GSjxFC89","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"The battle between President Obama and Mitt Romney reached new levels of rancor Thursday ,","depth":5},{"id":1,"text":"with each campaign accusing the other of lying over Romney 's tenure at private-equity firm Bain Capital .","depth":5},{"id":2,"text":"The charges flew at a rapid pace ,","depth":6},{"id":3,"text":"and by the end of the day the Romney campaign was calling for an apology","depth":7},{"id":4,"text":"after a senior Obama campaign official said","depth":8},{"id":5,"text":"the Republican presidential candidate may have committed a felony .","depth":8},{"id":6,"text":"Obama official Stephanie Cutter made the claim","depth":7},{"id":7,"text":"following a Boston Globe article","depth":8},{"id":8,"text":"that said","depth":9},{"id":9,"text":"documents show","depth":10},{"id":10,"text":"Romney was in charge at Bain for three years longer","depth":11},{"id":11,"text":"than he had claimed .","depth":11},{"id":12,"text":"Cutter said","depth":7},{"id":13,"text":"Romney was either misrepresenting his position at Bain to the Securities and Exchange Commission ,","depth":9},{"id":14,"text":"`` which is a felony , ''","depth":9},{"id":15,"text":"or misrepresenting to the American people .","depth":8},{"id":16,"text":"Romney campaign manager Matt Rhoades issued a blistering statement in response .","depth":4},{"id":17,"text":"`` President Obama 's campaign hit a new low today","depth":7},{"id":18,"text":"when one of its senior advisers made a reckless and unsubstantiated charge to reporters about Mitt Romney","depth":8},{"id":19,"text":"that was so over the top","depth":9},{"id":20,"text":"that it calls into question the integrity of their entire campaign , ''","depth":9},{"id":21,"text":"Rhoades said .","depth":6},{"id":22,"text":"`` President Obama ought to apologize for the out-of-control behavior of his staff ,","depth":7},{"id":23,"text":"which demeans the office","depth":8},{"id":24,"text":"he holds .","depth":8},{"id":25,"text":"Campaigns are supposed to be hard fought ,","depth":7},{"id":26,"text":"but statements like those","depth":9},{"id":27,"text":"made by Stephanie Cutter","depth":9},{"id":28,"text":"belittle the process and the candidate","depth":9},{"id":29,"text":"on whose behalf she works . ''","depth":9},{"id":30,"text":"The challenge capped a frenzied and nasty day on the campaign trail .","depth":3},{"id":31,"text":"Earlier , Romney released a new ad","depth":6},{"id":32,"text":"calling Obama dishonest","depth":7},{"id":33,"text":"and asking","depth":9},{"id":34,"text":"if the American people can `` trust him to lead ''","depth":9},{"id":35,"text":"if he `` does n't tell the truth . ''","depth":8},{"id":36,"text":"The release","depth":8},{"id":37,"text":"which accompanied the ad in an email to reporters","depth":8},{"id":38,"text":"also cited Obama 's `` lies and exaggerations . ''","depth":7},{"id":39,"text":"The ad","depth":9},{"id":40,"text":"titled , `` No Evidence , ''","depth":9},{"id":41,"text":"was an aggressive rebuttal to Obama 's claims","depth":9},{"id":42,"text":"that Romney outsourced jobs","depth":10},{"id":43,"text":"while at the helm of Bain Capital .","depth":10},{"id":44,"text":"`` There was no evidence","depth":9},{"id":45,"text":"that Mitt Romney shipped jobs overseas , ''","depth":9},{"id":46,"text":"a narrator says in the ad .","depth":8},{"id":47,"text":"But the Obama campaign pushed back in a statement","depth":7},{"id":48,"text":"charging","depth":8},{"id":49,"text":"the ad is part of Romney 's `` big Bain lie . ''","depth":8},{"id":50,"text":"Relying on the report in the Globe","depth":9},{"id":51,"text":"claiming","depth":10},{"id":52,"text":"government documents reveal","depth":11},{"id":53,"text":"Romney remained CEO of Bain for three years longer","depth":12},{"id":54,"text":"than he claimed ,","depth":12},{"id":55,"text":"the Obama camp statement went on to say","depth":8},{"id":56,"text":"the ad is `` based on a false premise . ''","depth":7},{"id":57,"text":"In a filing with the SEC in February 2001 , Bain Capital listed Romney as the company 's `` sole shareholder , sole director , chief executive officer and president . ''","depth":6},{"id":58,"text":"It said","depth":7},{"id":59,"text":"Romney 's `` principal occupation '' was as Bain 's managing director .","depth":7},{"id":60,"text":"Romney 's campaign repeatedly has said","depth":5},{"id":61,"text":"Romney had virtually nothing","depth":6},{"id":62,"text":"to do with the company 's operations after February 1999 ,","depth":7},{"id":63,"text":"when he began work on the troubled 2002 Winter Olympic Games .","depth":7},{"id":64,"text":"Questions about Romney 's control at Bain from 1999 to 2001 are important in his bid","depth":6},{"id":65,"text":"to oust Obama this fall .","depth":6},{"id":66,"text":"That 's when the company oversaw investments","depth":7},{"id":67,"text":"that either created jobs abroad","depth":8},{"id":68,"text":"or filed for bankruptcy .","depth":8},{"id":69,"text":"It 's also a time","depth":7},{"id":70,"text":"during which Romney stated in federal disclosure forms","depth":8},{"id":71,"text":"that he was not active in Bain Capital .","depth":8},{"id":72,"text":"Cutter , Obama 's deputy campaign manager , said","depth":5},{"id":73,"text":"Romney may have committed a felony","depth":6},{"id":74,"text":"if he misrepresented his role at Bain on the SEC documents .","depth":6},{"id":75,"text":"And","depth":6},{"id":76,"text":"if he was running Bain after 1999 ,","depth":8},{"id":77,"text":"Cutter said ,","depth":8},{"id":78,"text":"Romney has n't been truthful with the public .","depth":7},{"id":79,"text":"`` If that 's the case ,","depth":8},{"id":80,"text":"if he was lying to the American people ,","depth":8},{"id":81,"text":"then that 's a real character and trust issue , ''","depth":7},{"id":82,"text":"she said .","depth":6},{"id":83,"text":"But Romney 's campaign issued a statement Thursday from Bain","depth":4},{"id":84,"text":"that said","depth":6},{"id":85,"text":"Romney `` left Bain Capital in February 1999","depth":8},{"id":86,"text":"to run the Olympics","depth":8},{"id":87,"text":"and has had absolutely no involvement with the management or investment activities of the firm or with any of its portfolio companies since the day of his departure .","depth":7},{"id":88,"text":"Due to the sudden nature of Mr. Romney 's departure , he remained the sole stockholder for a time","depth":7},{"id":89,"text":"while formal ownership was being documented and transferred to the group of partners","depth":8},{"id":90,"text":"who took over management of the firm in 1999 .","depth":8},{"id":91,"text":"Accordingly , Mr. Romney was reported in various capacities on SEC filings during this period . ''","depth":6},{"id":92,"text":"J.W . Verrett , an attorney and assistant professor in economics , also told","depth":5},{"id":93,"text":"that the original Globe report appeared to `` be confused '' about the SEC filings .","depth":5},{"id":94,"text":"He noted","depth":6},{"id":95,"text":"they refer to `` Bain Capital VI , ''","depth":7},{"id":96,"text":"which he described","depth":8},{"id":97,"text":"as an investment separate from Bain Capital itself .","depth":8},{"id":98,"text":"`` Saying","depth":10},{"id":99,"text":"that Governor Romney was the CEO of Bain Capital VI","depth":10},{"id":100,"text":"is like saying","depth":10},{"id":101,"text":"that I am the CEO of my retirement account ...","depth":10},{"id":102,"text":"it 's a silly bit of legalese","depth":8},{"id":103,"text":"and it does n't also mean","depth":8},{"id":104,"text":"I am CEO of all the companies","depth":9},{"id":105,"text":"in which I invest , ''","depth":9},{"id":106,"text":"he said in an email .","depth":6}],"relations":[{"parent":213,"left":166,"right":212,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":166,"left":136,"right":165,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":136,"left":122,"righ